## ğŸ”¹ Variations of int & float

* **signed int** â†’ positive & negative both
* **unsigned int** â†’ only positive
* **short int** â†’ 2 bytes
* **long int** â†’ 8 bytes
* **long long int** â†’ 8 bytes
* **long double** â†’ 10 bytes
* **wchar\_t** â†’ 2 bytes (wide character)
* **void** â†’ no value (often return type of function)

